  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This field based, questionnaire study will document observational data on womens perception
      of menstrual bleeding in a cross-section of women in Sweden. Each subject will complete the
      questionnaire at one occasion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
